<title>UK: Higgs makes H1 loss, sees loss for full yr.</title>
<headline>Higgs makes H1 loss, sees loss for full yr.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-09-26</dateline>
<text>
<p>Half year to June 30</p>
<p>				 (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)	 loss 3.6		    vs 0.7 earnings</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	 1.0		    vs 1.0</p>
<p> Pretax		loss 1.8		    vs 0.5 profit</p>
<p> Turnover		 173.70		   vs 165.94</p>
<p>NOTE - Construction and property group Higgs &amp; Hill Plc said progress this year would still be overshadowed by difficulties within its construction division and the restructuring of its southern operations. Higgs said as result it would remain in loss for the current year.  </p>
<p> Operating loss	   1.24		   vs 0.82 profit</p>
